Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我贏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去東京的事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 基本上挺順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極她能做好報導的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極？你說報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒輪到她出場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傢伙也夠怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和日向也聊過 不知道她到底堅強還是軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和你一起打工的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 不過結月能把報導的事完美解決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}北海道的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別累壞自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是沒成功 你會很懊悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極挑戰…
