Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帶塊浮冰回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還不知道能不能帶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會發你些暖洋洋的照片的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在南極是不是鼻涕都會結冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想吃刨冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極真的埋著UFO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺就像要轉學了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見 搖搖布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}得暫時跟你告別了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也沒有別的送行方法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我沒想到會用這麼大排場嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨說要去南極的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家還當他笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都覺得是天方夜譚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且現在還是有人當他笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡也有三個多月沒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 只是不知道自己會是什麼心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不要太招搖比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有不少人嫌你們得意忘形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼好招搖的吧 明天就要出發啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話是這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是謠言傳得很兇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概是嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說你們為了籌錢去便利商店行竊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}經常去歌舞伎町陪男人鬼混…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是怎樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說 有人認為你們太跩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣出發真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回來後 說不定情況會更糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道說這個人就是小惠？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 日向還是第一次見到她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是和小理一起打工的三宅日向 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你剛才說的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是誰在那邊亂說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也只是聽說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對要把犯人抓出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天就要出發了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣胡說八道 怎麼能忍氣吞聲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在把事情鬧大也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們一直都對風言風語不理不睬的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}繼續無視就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可不一樣 這些都是假話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們哪有去新宿跟男人鬼混
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事實就是去過新宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才沒有鬼混
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能證明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠 你怎麼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你問我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每個人都有惡毒的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要以惡報惡 挺起胸膛做人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名言？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且現在在這裡的也不止你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有能傾吐不滿的對象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這個味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來下班途中喝一杯 就是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好咧 再來一罐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天發薪水 我請你們喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我還是很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是記仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是錯肯定在傳謠言的人身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}憑什麼我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂我懂 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想盡情大吼發洩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就吼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在寺廟後大吼大叫不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就去卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有一個小時 應該沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還沒去過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼大家敢做那麼丟人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大聲吼出來就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就當是餞別會啦 餞別會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠也要去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氣氛嗨起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小淵澤報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就高橋惠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的好友小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氣氛嗨起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小淵澤報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小淵澤報瀨 小淵澤報瀨 小淵澤報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康布丁體W7\bord0\fs65\frz274\frx338\fry4\1c&H6370CB&\be2\rnd8\move(1150,22,1144,402,0,658)}報{\1c&H64D8BD&}瀨{\1c&HCED9AA&}瘋{\1c&H3DDFEB&}了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:50.54,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康布丁體W7\bord0\fs65\frz274\frx338\fry4\1c&H6370CB&\be2\rnd8\move(1144,402,1142,62,0,2566)}報{\1c&H64D8BD&}瀨{\1c&HCED9AA&}瘋{\1c&H3DDFEB&}了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還好沒跟她們一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 最棒的一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒想到出發前一天還能來這麼一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想 自從決定去南極之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就沒什麼機會和你一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然小惠你好像不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那種事…算了 其實我也是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我心裡很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直都在想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想去遙遠的地方啦 不想待在這裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}討厭自己之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我為什麼會有這些想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概是因為小惠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我總是慢吞吞的 一直要小惠照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老是黏著你問東問西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有這回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我討厭這點 所以一直想改變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想黏在你身邊 不想當你口中的廢柴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少想成為你遊戲的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是怎樣 好豐盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼晚才回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就當送行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可不止那些喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來啦 雞蛋天國
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs20\1c&HB0A993&\frz4.023\pos(548,32)}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs20\1c&H6A6B6A&\frz3.948\be1\pos(484,174)}來吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走了 我走了 我走了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:16.87,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\fnGen Jyuu Gothic Heavy\fs80\xshad-5\1c&H4856A6&\3c&H354060&\4c&H3D4664&\frz2.458\frx348\fry0\pos(512,192)}在房間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:20.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fnGen Jyuu Gothic Heavy\fs80\xshad-5\1c&HAD8769&\3c&H354060&\4c&H756048&\frz2.458\pos(512,192)\frx334\fry358}出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要出發了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要在東京吃早餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不叫醒我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會加油不讓你擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 出發日早上來見你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我來和你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說和你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說你 還沒注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和南極去新宿的事 為什麼傳開來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和別人說過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你最初遇上南極時 為什麼高年級的知道她有100萬？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你還沒開口 你媽就知道你要去南極了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除了我還能是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還以為你很快會發現 然後大發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是真這麼以為的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:18:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是時間上的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是你跟南極她們都像個笨蛋一樣沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:16.79,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}そっと「会いたい」聞いた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:25.23,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}空に溶けて消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:42.81,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今も胸の奥　静かに揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:50.60,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}白く輝く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:58.94,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}残した足跡も消えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:07.02,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}果てないと思ってた時が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:15.40,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}終わりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:25.23,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}だからずっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:34.68,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}言葉より大切な思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:43.97,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}きっと繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:55.88,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いつの日か　また旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:07.41,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}だからずっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:17.04,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}一緒にいた　かけがえのない時が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:26.25,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}きっと繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:37.97,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いつまでも　いつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:43.22,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}またね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:16.79,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}聽見一聲輕輕的「想見你」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:25.23,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}聲音漸漸消失在了空中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:42.81,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我的心底依然在暗自動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:50.60,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}雪白閃耀的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:58.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我們踩下的足跡 漸漸褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:07.02,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}原以為這些時光 永無止境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:15.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}卻突然畫上了句號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:25.23,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以這份心情 我不會忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:34.68,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}它比任何語言 都要寶貴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:43.97,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}總有一天 會再度牽起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:55.88,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}帶著我們 又一次踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:07.41,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以這些時光 我不會忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:17.04,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}你我一道 度過的珍貴點滴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:26.25,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}想必它們 會永遠牽起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:37.97,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}直到永遠 直到永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:43.22,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一開始跟我說要去南極的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就在想為什麼我會這麼生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理以前不管做什麼都會先找我商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}騙人的吧 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉讓你留下不好的回憶 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天聽你一說 我才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直黏著人的不是你 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你會依靠我 會找我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就會裝出一副 拿你沒轍只好幫幫你的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總是什麼都明白似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為不這麼做 我就一無所有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:20:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為自己一無所有 所以想讓你也一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}廢柴的不是你 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必須走出這個小世界的 是我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說什麼傻話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我終於打算向 沒有你的世界前進了啊
